<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.infidels.org/library/modern/richard_carrier/heaven.html" class="external text" title="http://www.infidels.org/library/modern/richard_carrier/heaven.html" rel="nofollow">The End of Pascal's Wager: Only Nontheists Go to Heaven (2002)</a> by <a href="/wiki/Richard_Carrier" title="Richard Carrier">Richard Carrier</a></li>
