<li><a href="http://www.philosophyofreligion.info/theistic-proofs/pascals-wager/the-atheists-wager/" class="external text" title="http://www.philosophyofreligion.info/theistic-proofs/pascals-wager/the-atheists-wager/" rel="nofollow">Pascal's Wager: The Atheist's Wager</a></li>
</ul>
